## What This Scenario Does

{{ scenario.name }} targets the {{ scenario.scope }} coverage gap through a parameterised intervention designed to improve connectivity for the most underserved communities. The {{ scenario.population_affected|int|format_thousands }} affected residents currently experience service levels below the threshold associated with adequate connectivity for employment, healthcare, and social participation.

